Modification notice (2026-07-14):

The upstream Skill was extracted into an independent Skill named
"compress-image". The multi-backend Bun/TypeScript implementation was replaced
with a Node.js CLI using pinned Sharp 0.34.5. The supported scope is static PNG,
JPEG, and WebP input with WebP or lossless PNG output. Source images are kept by
default, output writes are staged through temporary files, and replacement
requires an explicit --replace option. The upstream EXTEND.md convention,
JPEG output, GIF/TIFF input, and system-tool backend selection were removed.

The installable Skill is packaged under compress-image/. Repository-level
documentation, tests, and CI remain at the repository root. LICENSE and NOTICE
are copied into the installable Skill so attribution travels with installation.

Runtime dependency:

  Project: Sharp
  Version: 0.34.5
  Repository: https://github.com/lovell/sharp
  License: Apache License 2.0

Sharp is installed from npm into the user's cache on first use and is not
vendored in this repository.
